  "title": "[FLINK-2406] [FLINK-2402] Abstract the BarrierBuffers and add a \"at least once\" version (BarrierTracker)",
  "user": {
    "login": "StephanEwen",
    "id": 1727146,
    "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE3MjcxNDY=",
